Pico 3 active firmware: painting rotation puzzle.

This folder is the active Pico 3 project. The old TV wall trigger code is archived in:

../../pico6-unused-future-puzzles/unused-future-puzzles/

Hardware:
- GPIO 15: RC35 magnetic sensor, reed switch, or equivalent hall-style sensor

Main topics:
- Publishes escape/pico3/painting_rotation_complete every time the enabled sensor is freshly triggered
- Subscribes escape/cmd/pico3/enable_painting_rotation
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/status_request
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/reset_puzzle

The Raspberry Pi plays assets/audio/crashing_plates.m4a each time this event is received.
